Package: TreatmentPatterns
Type: Package
Title: Analyzes Real-World Treatment Patterns of a Study Population of Interest
Version: 2.5.0
Author: Aniek F Markus
Maintainer: Maarten van Kessel <m.l.vankessel@erasmusmc.nl>
Description:
